# BackBork Logs Directory
#
# This directory contains operation logs and backup job logs.
# Created at runtime by BackBork.
#
# Files stored here:
#   - operations.log              : Main JSON-lines log for GUI display (all operations)
#   - backup_{timestamp}_{id}.log : Per-backup detailed logs with pkgacct output
#   - restore_{timestamp}_{id}.log: Per-restore detailed logs
#
# operations.log format (JSON lines):
# {"timestamp":"2026-01-10 12:00:00","user":"root","type":"backup_local","items":["account1"],"success":true,"message":"Backup completed","requestor":"cron"}
#
# Backup logs contain real-time pkgacct/mariadb-backup output for troubleshooting.
#
# Log rotation: Logs older than 30 days are removed by the cleanup cron task.
